The Bhoy Who Would Be King is a fitting tribute to Henrik Larsson&#039;s remarkable career as a fully fledged Celtic hero
and a celebration of the exciting Swede&#039;s prolific goal scoring record.
Over the past years, Larsson&#039;s phenomenal career with Celtic has brought untold joy to millions of Hoops fans worldwide
and this programme charts his progression at Celtic beginning August 1997 through to the 2003/04 Season.
